text: Pauline Jannault-Lo , (born 13 January 1987 Ermont), is a French basketball player playing as an outside hitter. She competed at the 2010 FIBA Women's World Championship. She played for Tarbes., Perpignan, Bourges, and Toulouse.. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:French basketball players Category:Women's basketball players
